description: Returns a list of databases in a server.

api_version.description: The API version to use for the request.

subscription_id.description: The subscription ID that identifies an Azure subscription.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group that contains the resource. You can obtain this value from the Azure Resource Manager API or the portal.

expand.description: A comma separated list of child objects to expand in the response. Possible properties: serviceTierAdvisors, transparentDataEncryption.

filter.description: An OData filter expression that describes a subset of databases to return.

value.description: The list of databases housed in the server.
